WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 19=

01:44.900 --> 01:45.740
Milady.

01:45.930 --> 01:48.180
Did Mr. Chang upset you?.

01:50.260 --> 01:51.100
No.

01:51.620 --> 01:52.460
Don't mention him.

01:55.930 --> 01:57.100
Something feels off.

01:59.490 --> 02:00.740
Alright, I'm tired.

02:00.740 --> 02:01.580
Gonna sleep.

02:05.490 --> 02:07.100
Something's off. Something's off.

02:08.690 --> 02:09.820
Something's off.

02:11.500 --> 02:12.580
(Carefree)

02:12.580 --> 02:13.460
When

02:13.850 --> 02:15.170
the Young Master arrives later,

02:15.730 --> 02:17.130
everyone smile.

02:17.130 --> 02:18.340
Make it cheerful

02:18.340 --> 02:19.200
and sweet.

02:19.200 --> 02:20.540
Make our Young Master

02:20.540 --> 02:22.260
so happy

02:22.260 --> 02:24.220
he's over the moon.

02:24.220 --> 02:25.610
Make him so happy

02:25.610 --> 02:27.220
he's over the moon.

02:27.220 --> 02:28.060
Smile.

02:29.380 --> 02:31.060
Master You, if you're tired of living,

02:31.500 --> 02:32.380
just say so.

02:33.500 --> 02:34.340
Mr. Mu.

02:34.660 --> 02:35.690
Mr. Mu.

02:36.220 --> 02:37.220
Mr. Mu, calm down.

02:37.220 --> 02:38.340
Elder Yan said

02:38.340 --> 02:39.780
you've been working hard.

02:39.780 --> 02:41.260
It's unwise to be without a maid.

02:41.260 --> 02:42.260
We picked some

02:42.260 --> 02:44.100
cheerful girls.

02:44.100 --> 02:45.100
Mr. Mu, just choose one.

02:48.730 --> 02:49.570
Mr. Mu.

02:50.060 --> 02:51.980
I'm from Qinglong Altar.

02:51.980 --> 02:53.570
Long heard of your fame.

02:53.570 --> 02:54.980
Seeing you today,

02:54.980 --> 02:57.290
a poem popped into my head.

02:57.290 --> 02:59.170
"A face that charms,
a soul like orchids."

02:59.170 --> 03:01.100
"So bold and bright,
all blooms are swayed."

03:01.100 --> 03:02.540
Poetry on the spot.

03:03.500 --> 03:04.570
What a talent.

03:14.410 --> 03:15.850
I'm from Xuanwu Altar.

03:15.850 --> 03:17.260
I don't know much.

03:17.260 --> 03:19.220
All need your guidance, Mr. Mu.

03:19.220 --> 03:20.060
Mr. Mu.

03:20.060 --> 03:21.340
Your robe is wrinkled.

03:21.340 --> 03:22.290
Let me take it back.

03:22.290 --> 03:24.100
I'll iron it with heated blue stone.

03:25.610 --> 03:27.340
Dutiful and virtuous.

03:27.940 --> 03:30.500
This fabric is amazing.

03:35.780 --> 03:36.780
Take them all.

03:37.890 --> 03:38.780
All of them?

03:40.690 --> 03:41.570
Mr. Mu.

03:41.570 --> 03:42.660
Elder Yan said

03:42.660 --> 03:44.890
you can only pick one.

03:44.890 --> 03:45.730
One?

03:49.610 --> 03:50.450
Fine.

03:51.010 --> 03:52.100
Then I choose Xing.

03:54.220 --> 03:55.100
Come on, leave now.

03:55.290 --> 03:56.130
Hurry, leave!

03:56.380 --> 03:57.850
Mr. Mu doesn't need servants anymore.

04:01.470 --> 04:02.380
One.

04:02.380 --> 04:04.010
Zhao, tell us.

04:04.010 --> 04:04.980
What's the demon sect like?

04:04.980 --> 04:05.820
Zhao.

04:05.820 --> 04:07.570
Do they really

04:07.570 --> 04:09.010
eat raw meat and drink blood daily?

04:09.020 --> 04:09.940
- Three.
- Yeah.

04:09.940 --> 04:10.780
Yes.

04:10.940 --> 04:11.980
They're much like us.

04:12.360 --> 04:13.380
- Work at sunrise.
- One.

04:13.380 --> 04:14.570
Rest at sunset.

04:15.100 --> 04:17.370
After harvest,
they trade at the marketplace.

04:17.370 --> 04:18.490
They're just ordinary folk.

04:18.700 --> 04:19.540
Just like us?

04:22.490 --> 04:23.370
These ordinary folk

04:23.370 --> 04:25.140
killed tens of thousands of
our Six Sects' disciples.

04:25.410 --> 04:26.580
Their hands are stained red.

04:27.170 --> 04:29.780
Nie Zhe and Mu Qingyan
are ruthless monsters.

04:29.780 --> 04:31.290
They should've died together long ago.

04:31.290 --> 04:32.700
That's too harsh..

04:32.700 --> 04:34.020
Nie Zhe defies all order.

04:34.020 --> 04:35.610
He deserves death for human trials.

04:36.850 --> 04:38.340
But not everyone in the demon sect

04:39.140 --> 04:40.370
is deserving of such condemnation.

04:40.370 --> 04:41.210
Zhao,

04:41.490 --> 04:43.050
why are you defending those devils?

04:43.050 --> 04:44.170
Forgot how your aunt, Ms. Cai,

04:44.170 --> 04:45.410
died?

04:45.410 --> 04:47.220
How the Chang clan was wiped out?

04:47.220 --> 04:48.730
You go out to gather some news

04:48.730 --> 04:50.610
and come back forgetting
you're a Six Sects disciple.

04:54.610 --> 04:55.450
I just think

04:55.810 --> 04:57.290
good and evil aren't black and white.

04:57.290 --> 04:59.540
Not all demon sect members are evil.

04:59.730 --> 05:00.570
Likewise,

05:01.100 --> 05:03.410
the Six Sects have
their share of scoundrels too.

05:11.300 --> 05:14.740
(Zhuo)

05:31.100 --> 05:31.940
Milady.

05:35.140 --> 05:36.660
What's wrong?

05:36.660 --> 05:38.930
You were fine when you left.

05:39.490 --> 05:41.170
I want wontons.

05:42.580 --> 05:44.160
Milady, didn't you say

05:44.170 --> 05:45.610
you'd never eat wontons again?

05:48.340 --> 05:49.490
Did I?

05:49.980 --> 05:50.820
Alright.

06:03.100 --> 06:03.940
Zhao.

06:08.930 --> 06:09.770
Zhao.

06:13.020 --> 06:13.860
Master.

06:14.220 --> 06:15.540
I have something to tell you.

06:19.020 --> 06:19.860
Come.

06:20.250 --> 06:21.090
Sit down.

06:24.250 --> 06:26.780
This time,
coming back from the Hanhai Mountains,

06:27.610 --> 06:29.780
do you feel that
not everyone in the demon sect

06:29.780 --> 06:31.930
is a monster?

06:32.370 --> 06:34.220
Some might even be good at heart.

06:37.810 --> 06:39.170
Remember when you were little,

06:40.140 --> 06:41.780
the story Pingshu told you

06:41.780 --> 06:43.100
about the skin-painted demon?

06:43.850 --> 06:44.690
I remember that.

06:45.290 --> 06:46.250
My aunt once said

06:48.100 --> 06:49.100
the skin-painted demon

06:49.540 --> 06:51.050
is a creature with a twisted face,

06:51.050 --> 06:52.810
a bloodthirsty being without restraint.

06:54.070 --> 06:55.540
It eats live human hearts and livers,

06:56.220 --> 06:57.900
uses human skin to deceive people.

06:58.250 --> 06:59.810
A skin-painted demon,
wearing human skin,

07:00.580 --> 07:01.810
looks just like anyone else.

07:02.720 --> 07:03.880
And they can seem even more

07:04.100 --> 07:05.490
understanding

07:05.620 --> 07:06.780
and caring
than real people.

07:23.290 --> 07:25.290
Before showing its bleeding fangs,

07:27.050 --> 07:29.020
it will watch operas with you,

07:29.020 --> 07:29.860
taste wine,

07:30.610 --> 07:32.170
chat and laugh by your side,

07:32.170 --> 07:34.730
even wait two hours
outside Yipin Pavilion

07:34.730 --> 07:36.780
just to buy a fresh roasted pigeon

07:36.780 --> 07:37.850
to satisfy your craving.

07:55.780 --> 07:57.490
But a demon is a demon.

07:58.020 --> 07:58.860
It's a demon.

07:59.250 --> 08:00.410
It feeds on human flesh

08:00.810 --> 08:01.930
and drinks human blood.

08:06.610 --> 08:08.020
Can you imagine it?

08:08.540 --> 08:09.980
Your dearest friend...

08:09.980 --> 08:10.820
I'm here.

08:11.100 --> 08:12.730
Killed by the skin-painted demon,

08:14.050 --> 08:15.700
dying with eyes wide open.

08:26.020 --> 08:26.860
Master.

08:27.540 --> 08:28.810
Jianghu is treacherous.

08:29.340 --> 08:30.660
It's far more cruel

08:31.340 --> 08:32.580
than you think.

08:34.220 --> 08:35.370
Don't make your aunt

08:36.980 --> 08:37.940
worry about you.

08:42.370 --> 08:43.210
Aunt.

08:45.730 --> 08:47.300
Is the skin-painted demon

08:48.100 --> 08:48.940
Master talked about

08:48.940 --> 08:51.100
the masked guy who went to
Snow Mountain with aunt?

08:53.580 --> 08:54.420
Zhao.

08:55.420 --> 08:56.530
You've always been obedient.

08:56.850 --> 08:57.980
You must remember

08:57.980 --> 08:59.220
what Master said.

09:00.220 --> 09:01.060
A demon

09:02.180 --> 09:03.940
always eats people.

09:15.490 --> 09:16.330
Uncle Lei,

09:17.850 --> 09:19.610
do you know the skin-painted demon?

09:21.220 --> 09:22.340
The skin-painted demon…

09:23.220 --> 09:24.890
I don't know who he is,

09:25.650 --> 09:26.610
but I do know of him.

09:26.840 --> 09:27.780
Were the skin-painted demon

09:28.300 --> 09:29.610
and my aunt

09:30.340 --> 09:31.490
definitely close?

09:32.010 --> 09:33.010
Your aunt

09:33.010 --> 09:34.610
never mentioned his name,

09:35.940 --> 09:38.100
but one year
she asked Granny Needle Zhuo

09:38.100 --> 09:39.420
to embroider a wrist guard.

09:40.980 --> 09:42.490
From its size,

09:43.530 --> 09:44.980
it was for a man.

09:45.700 --> 09:47.700
But isn't Uncle Zhou doing well?

09:47.700 --> 09:48.610
Yes, he is.

09:49.250 --> 09:50.490
But they

09:50.490 --> 09:51.610
can't make it work.

09:52.850 --> 09:54.650
To be honest,

09:54.650 --> 09:55.700
Uncle Zhou's character,

09:55.700 --> 09:57.300
talents and family background

09:57.300 --> 09:58.370
are great.

09:58.370 --> 10:00.220
He and your aunt
were childhood sweethearts,

10:01.130 --> 10:01.980
but

10:02.580 --> 10:04.300
he never truly understood what Pingshu

10:04.300 --> 10:05.820
wanted for her life.

10:06.530 --> 10:08.610
He's gentle and compromising.

10:08.610 --> 10:09.770
And when faced with injustice,

10:10.150 --> 10:11.250
he endured and lets it pass.

10:11.730 --> 10:12.940
Then he hoped others

10:13.980 --> 10:15.730
would also take a step back
and find peace.

10:19.370 --> 10:21.890
My aunt isn't one to swallow her anger.

10:23.240 --> 10:24.820
She's like clear wind and blazing fire.

10:25.420 --> 10:26.820
Clear wind caresses the mountains.

10:27.610 --> 10:29.060
Blazing fire burns all demons.

10:32.820 --> 10:33.660
Master.

10:35.220 --> 10:36.100
Those words

10:36.520 --> 10:37.980
were actually spoken by your Master.

10:39.370 --> 10:41.700
My Master would say something like that?

10:41.700 --> 10:43.130
Lord seems dull,
but he's brilliant within.

10:44.850 --> 10:46.180
After the Righteous-Demonic War,

10:47.320 --> 10:48.730
the Six Sects suffered heavy losses.

10:49.220 --> 10:50.980
Yet within a short span of time,

10:50.980 --> 10:52.130
your Master steadied the Six Sects

10:52.130 --> 10:53.300
and intimidated the demon sect,

10:54.300 --> 10:56.180
bringing peace to Jianghu
for over ten years.

10:56.180 --> 10:57.770
What great strategy.

11:02.730 --> 11:04.850
He brought up that story out of nowhere.

11:06.250 --> 11:07.890
Is it because of Chang Ning?

11:14.060 --> 11:15.530
How's the poison in his body?

11:16.220 --> 11:17.610
Uncle's medicine

11:18.610 --> 11:19.890
suppressed it temporarily.

11:20.420 --> 11:21.260
He won't die.

11:22.010 --> 11:22.850
Temporary suppression

11:24.060 --> 11:25.250
means it'll come back.

11:27.610 --> 11:28.850
From now on,

11:30.250 --> 11:31.580
Zhao, you truly can let him go?

11:34.850 --> 11:36.060
Pretend he never existed.

11:44.730 --> 11:45.570
This time,

11:46.300 --> 11:47.530
listen to your Master.

11:48.980 --> 11:49.940
Fate

11:50.340 --> 11:51.370
can't be forced.

11:52.100 --> 11:53.100
Let it go when it's gone.

12:06.370 --> 12:08.220
I'll go get a new one from Xingjia.

12:22.530 --> 12:23.440
Mr. Mu,

12:23.450 --> 12:24.850
don't be reckless!

12:25.980 --> 12:27.890
The matter between Mr. Mu and Miss Cai

12:27.890 --> 12:29.980
has unsettled the Li Sect.

12:29.980 --> 12:30.820
Mr. Mu,

12:30.820 --> 12:32.650
to hold the Chief's seat firmly,

12:32.650 --> 12:34.340
you must marry a sect member

12:34.340 --> 12:35.650
and have children

12:35.650 --> 12:37.890
to stabilize people's hearts.

12:37.890 --> 12:39.700
I think even the village chief's boar

12:39.700 --> 12:41.130
could do that too.

12:41.130 --> 12:42.420
Elder Yan, Why don't you

12:42.420 --> 12:43.820
ask it to be Chief?

12:44.980 --> 12:46.250
Mr. Mu,

12:46.250 --> 12:48.630
are you still hung up on that Cai girl?

12:48.630 --> 12:49.490
Not only

12:49.490 --> 12:51.220
is she Cai Pingshu's niece,

12:51.380 --> 12:52.770
but the Li Sect and Six Sects

12:52.770 --> 12:54.180
have a 200-year-long blood feud.

12:54.180 --> 12:55.530
Irreconcilable!

12:55.530 --> 12:56.610
Remember

12:56.610 --> 12:59.250
what happened to

12:59.250 --> 13:00.650
the powerful
Chief Mu Donglie in the end?

13:01.580 --> 13:02.420
Mr. Mu,

13:02.770 --> 13:04.370
do you not remember it?

13:05.220 --> 13:06.300
Mr. Mu, you…

13:07.530 --> 13:08.370
Elder Yan, Elder Yan.

13:08.650 --> 13:09.490
I just remembered

13:09.620 --> 13:10.940
Shangguan got a jar of fine wine.

13:10.940 --> 13:12.650
Let's go drink it all now.

13:12.650 --> 13:13.890
– Let's go, drink.
– Mr. Mu.

13:13.890 --> 13:14.770
I haven't finished.

13:14.770 --> 13:15.890
Go, go, go.

13:16.730 --> 13:18.370
Drink, Elder Yan.

13:18.370 --> 13:20.130
- Come on.
- Why drink? Stop pushing.

13:20.890 --> 13:22.060
- Let me go.
- Elder Yan.

13:22.060 --> 13:23.700
For the grand future of Li Sect, I'll...

13:23.700 --> 13:24.580
Elder Yan.

13:25.300 --> 13:27.130
You really hit a nerve this time.

13:28.010 --> 13:29.250
Miss Cai and the Young Master

13:29.250 --> 13:31.580
are like the Cowboy and Weaver stars
in the sky now.

13:31.580 --> 13:33.530
Separated by the celestial river,
each in sorrow.

13:34.250 --> 13:36.100
Why do you have to hurt him?

13:37.300 --> 13:38.370
Miss Cai

13:39.130 --> 13:40.700
is probably hiding somewhere crying.

13:54.370 --> 13:55.370
So many.

13:55.370 --> 13:56.370
All for me?

13:57.890 --> 13:58.940
Yuzhi said

13:58.940 --> 14:00.890
thanks to you
finding the hot spring stone.

14:00.890 --> 14:01.730
These small gifts

14:01.730 --> 14:03.940
hardly express Uncle Song's gratitude.

14:03.940 --> 14:04.950
Even ten times as much

14:04.950 --> 14:05.940
would still be only fitting.

14:07.340 --> 14:08.180
Indeed.

14:10.220 --> 14:11.340
Yuzhi's inner power

14:11.340 --> 14:12.650
has recovered seventy to eighty percent.

14:12.940 --> 14:13.780
Unfortunately,

14:14.060 --> 14:15.340
there's still some cold energy

14:15.340 --> 14:16.770
in his dantian.

14:16.770 --> 14:17.770
Hard to fully purge.

14:18.580 --> 14:20.820
I'll definitely find the Jade Sunflower
for Yuzhi

14:21.300 --> 14:23.220
to remove the remaining cold energy.

14:23.220 --> 14:24.060
Father, don't worry.

14:24.370 --> 14:25.220
Alright.

14:25.220 --> 14:26.060
I don't worry.

14:26.980 --> 14:27.820
Zhao,

14:28.220 --> 14:29.370
you're young,

14:29.370 --> 14:30.610
yet brave and sharp.

14:30.610 --> 14:31.940
Truly worthy of being Pingshu's niece.

14:33.060 --> 14:34.180
If only
you'd been betrothed

14:34.180 --> 14:35.220
to Yuzhi, that'd be great.

14:35.220 --> 14:36.060
Father.

14:36.370 --> 14:37.210
I... I...

14:37.530 --> 14:39.180
We should thank Zhao

14:39.890 --> 14:41.890
for finding the stone to heal my cousin.

14:48.700 --> 14:49.610
Zhao.

14:49.610 --> 14:51.610
Here's nourishing soup
made by Nanny Mao.

14:51.610 --> 14:52.890
You just returned from your travels.

14:52.890 --> 14:53.820
Need to recharge.

14:54.370 --> 14:55.210
Thank you, Lingbo.

15:12.300 --> 15:13.140
Dear.

15:15.730 --> 15:16.730
Dear, today,

15:17.730 --> 15:19.370
why didn't you go pray?

15:19.370 --> 15:21.340
I copied a scripture for you
in the temple.

15:22.020 --> 15:23.980
Reading it can calm the mind
and ease the spirit.

15:23.980 --> 15:24.940
It will aid your cultivation.

15:25.890 --> 15:26.820
Thank you, Dear.

15:29.010 --> 15:30.250
I heard from Shijun

15:31.010 --> 15:33.370
that Yuzhi's inner power
has mostly returned.

15:33.370 --> 15:34.220
So

15:34.220 --> 15:35.770
why not double the joy?

15:35.770 --> 15:37.060
With him here,

15:37.060 --> 15:38.060
let's fix the kids' wedding

15:38.060 --> 15:39.820
in the next few days.

15:41.370 --> 15:42.370
Dear,

15:42.370 --> 15:43.420
Nie Zhe has gone missing.

15:43.420 --> 15:44.580
The demon sect has a new leader.

15:44.580 --> 15:46.060
We don't know what the new Chief

15:46.060 --> 15:47.580
thinks of the Six Sects,

15:48.060 --> 15:49.820
or if he has any plans.

15:50.220 --> 15:52.250
This may not be the best time.

15:52.980 --> 15:53.820
Besides,

15:54.530 --> 15:55.770
are Yuzhi and Lingbo

15:56.370 --> 15:57.850
truly a good match?

15:57.850 --> 15:59.180
Marriage

15:59.180 --> 16:00.940
is decided by elders.

16:00.940 --> 16:02.530
If we think they suit each other,

16:02.530 --> 16:04.010
then they must be well matched.

16:05.010 --> 16:06.300
As parents,

16:06.300 --> 16:08.490
who wouldn't wish the best
for their children?

16:20.890 --> 16:21.730
Lingbo,

16:24.530 --> 16:25.370
where are you going?

16:25.980 --> 16:27.180
I'm just in the way here.

16:27.740 --> 16:29.730
Guess I'll go down
and carve out my own path.

16:30.220 --> 16:31.060
Save

16:31.300 --> 16:32.180
everyone the trouble.

16:32.610 --> 16:34.180
The demon sect just finished infighting.

16:34.420 --> 16:35.580
The situation is unclear.

16:35.840 --> 16:37.420
Going down the mountain now
is too risky.

16:37.730 --> 16:39.650
Why can Cai Zhao go down to find saliva

16:39.890 --> 16:40.820
and rare stones,

16:40.820 --> 16:41.660
but I can't?

16:42.180 --> 16:43.020
Lingbo,

16:44.030 --> 16:45.100
why compare yourself to her?

16:45.420 --> 16:47.250
Do you think
I'm not as good as Cai Zhao?

16:47.730 --> 16:48.820
Are you like Father

16:48.820 --> 16:50.100
and cousin,

16:50.100 --> 16:51.130
thinking she's the best?

16:51.130 --> 16:52.010
In my heart,

16:52.010 --> 16:52.980
you're the best.

16:52.980 --> 16:54.340
Ten Cai Zhaos can't compare to you.

16:57.250 --> 16:58.090
Cut the sweet talk.

16:58.650 --> 16:59.610
I'm not a child anymore.

17:00.940 --> 17:01.780
I know.

17:02.730 --> 17:04.090
Lingbo, you have your own thoughts.

17:05.570 --> 17:06.770
I won't stop you by force.

17:07.380 --> 17:08.860
But if you want to leave the mountain,

17:08.860 --> 17:10.290
you must first tell Master and Lady Yin.

17:11.050 --> 17:12.010
I'll go with you.

17:12.810 --> 17:13.660
Let's go together.

17:35.860 --> 17:36.700
So

17:36.700 --> 17:38.570
Lingbo plans to leave the mountain,

17:38.570 --> 17:40.090
and it's because of Zhao.

17:40.380 --> 17:41.940
Zhao first saved our sect,

17:42.220 --> 17:44.180
then found a rare stone to heal Yuzhi.

17:44.620 --> 17:46.570
No wonder Yuzhi was moved by her.

17:47.490 --> 17:48.420
But I remember

17:48.940 --> 17:50.700
Zhao already has a fiancé.

17:52.700 --> 17:54.010
Why speak such plain truths aloud?

17:55.010 --> 17:56.570
Don't stir more trouble in the sect.

18:00.050 --> 18:01.010
Yuzhi.

18:01.010 --> 18:02.660
Knew you two tried to elope.

18:02.660 --> 18:03.500
Still not admitting it.

18:03.510 --> 18:05.420
The whole sect's talking about it.

18:05.420 --> 18:07.330
They said you and Zhao failed to elope

18:07.330 --> 18:08.530
and were forced to come back.

18:08.530 --> 18:10.140
Lingbo was so mad
she almost jumped off a cliff.

18:10.140 --> 18:11.420
Luckily, Fengchi stopped her.

18:11.900 --> 18:12.860
But

18:12.860 --> 18:14.530
Yuzhi, don't let it
trouble you too much.

18:15.290 --> 18:16.860
I think Lingbo

18:16.860 --> 18:18.290
was just venting her temper.

18:18.290 --> 18:20.180
If she truly wanted to end her life,

18:20.180 --> 18:21.620
how could she be stopped so easily?

18:21.980 --> 18:22.980
Besides,

18:22.980 --> 18:24.220
Fengchi follows Lingbo

18:24.220 --> 18:25.660
everywhere.

18:25.660 --> 18:27.660
Everyone in Qingque Sect
knows how he feels.

18:28.250 --> 18:29.980
This is the perfect time to tell Master.

18:30.080 --> 18:31.050
Happy ending for everyone!

18:32.050 --> 18:33.810
I think you and Zhao

18:33.810 --> 18:35.700
are a perfect match.

18:35.700 --> 18:36.620
Made for each other.

18:37.050 --> 18:38.010
This time, you...

18:38.010 --> 18:39.290
These absurd rumors

18:39.290 --> 18:40.490
are bad for Zhao,

18:40.490 --> 18:41.770
Fengchi

18:41.770 --> 18:42.620
and Lingbo.

18:43.010 --> 18:44.660
Looks like the whole sect

18:44.660 --> 18:45.500
needs some discipline.

18:46.220 --> 18:47.770
What's the big deal?

18:47.770 --> 18:49.330
We all think you two make a fine pair.

18:49.620 --> 18:50.460
Xingjia.

18:52.730 --> 18:53.660
As for my marriage.

18:53.920 --> 18:55.770
There's no need for the whole sect
to worry about it.

18:56.010 --> 18:57.250
Zhao, why are you...

18:57.770 --> 18:58.610
here?

18:58.900 --> 19:00.330
Yuzhi and I are just pure friends.

19:00.330 --> 19:01.330
We stay within bounds.

19:01.770 --> 19:03.570
How could such nonsense about eloping

19:03.570 --> 19:05.140
spread to sully our reputations?

19:05.990 --> 19:06.980
Xingjia, it's fine you don't

19:06.980 --> 19:08.900
investigate where the rumors started.

19:08.900 --> 19:11.140
But you actually join in
with this nonsense.

19:11.140 --> 19:12.290
It's unbearable.

19:12.290 --> 19:13.380
Zh... Zhao.

19:13.730 --> 19:15.420
I misspoke.

19:15.420 --> 19:16.420
Don't be mad.

19:16.750 --> 19:18.090
Rumors with no basis

19:18.330 --> 19:19.530
always die down.

19:19.860 --> 19:21.050
I'm afraid the rumors

19:21.050 --> 19:22.220
are getting out of hand.

19:25.020 --> 19:25.860
I heard

19:25.860 --> 19:27.660
Yuzhi and Cai Zhao eloped together.

19:27.660 --> 19:28.500
Is that true?

19:28.760 --> 19:30.620
I also heard
she took on the demon sect alone,

19:30.620 --> 19:32.220
no less than Ms. Cai back in her prime.

19:32.220 --> 19:33.860
No wonder Yuzhi admires her.

19:36.090 --> 19:37.420
Who? Who struck me from behind?

19:37.420 --> 19:39.140
Early in the morning, you gossipers

19:39.140 --> 19:40.330
are jabbering nonsense

19:40.330 --> 19:41.170
and stirring up trouble.

19:41.730 --> 19:42.730
How about I see

19:42.730 --> 19:44.250
how your morning training's
coming along?

19:44.490 --> 19:45.700
No, wait.

19:45.700 --> 19:46.660
Cai Zhao, what are you doing?

19:47.330 --> 19:48.980
Zhao just joined the Qingque Sect,

19:48.980 --> 19:50.860
yet you already
exposed the demon sect's disguise.

19:50.860 --> 19:53.330
Then spied on them
for half a month to gather intel.

19:53.330 --> 19:54.700
Truly heroic.

19:55.380 --> 19:57.380
I want to learn from you too.

19:57.380 --> 19:58.860
Enough with the nonsense.

20:05.910 --> 20:06.770
Cai Zhao!

20:06.770 --> 20:08.570
Why use the Sunshine Blade
for a sect duel?

20:08.570 --> 20:10.010
If you've got the skill,
attack together.

20:10.010 --> 20:11.050
If not, stay out of my way.

20:11.050 --> 20:11.900
Cai Zhao!

20:11.900 --> 20:12.860
Don't push us too far!

20:13.860 --> 20:15.330
You asked for this.

20:29.810 --> 20:31.330
Zhao's 36th Form of the Sunshine Blade

20:31.330 --> 20:32.220
are brilliant.

20:32.520 --> 20:33.570
I humbly seek your guidance.

20:34.120 --> 20:35.330
Yuzhi, please make your move.

20:40.090 --> 20:42.330
Yuzhi's using himself as a punching bag

20:42.570 --> 20:44.140
to let Zhao vent.

20:46.940 --> 20:47.780
Zhao.

20:50.490 --> 20:51.330
Yuqi.

20:51.520 --> 20:52.500
Haven't seen you in days.

20:52.750 --> 20:54.570
Zhao, your martial arts
have improved even more.

20:57.380 --> 20:58.900
Congratulations on recovering, Yuzhi.

20:59.250 --> 21:00.330
Yuzhi's skills truly

21:00.330 --> 21:01.980
make you the top of
the Six Sects' new generation.

21:02.900 --> 21:04.330
You flatter me, Young Lord Zhou.

21:04.330 --> 21:05.180
Young Lord Zhou,

21:05.810 --> 21:07.700
your fiancée is about to be taken away.

21:07.700 --> 21:08.620
If I were you,

21:08.620 --> 21:10.420
I'd duel him fair and square.

21:10.900 --> 21:11.740
Utter nonsense.

21:11.900 --> 21:12.940
Who'd buy that?

21:13.620 --> 21:15.140
Fengchi, if you can't talk sense,

21:15.140 --> 21:17.250
better sharpen your martial arts.

21:21.140 --> 21:21.980
You okay?

21:23.620 --> 21:24.460
I'm fine.

21:35.120 --> 21:36.980
Zhou Yuqi's just here to
push for the wedding.

21:37.700 --> 21:38.980
That guy usually

21:38.980 --> 21:40.530
keeps a low profile.

21:40.530 --> 21:41.660
Yet this time, he acted fast.

21:43.090 --> 21:44.420
I told you long ago,

21:44.420 --> 21:46.050
you and Lingbo aren't a good match.

21:46.050 --> 21:47.420
I should've ended
the engagement for you.

21:47.420 --> 21:49.690
Then I wouldn't be this anxious now.

21:49.710 --> 21:50.570
But you

21:50.570 --> 21:52.180
insisted on handling it alone.

21:52.180 --> 21:54.090
You're too stubborn.

21:55.940 --> 21:57.180
If you don't act soon,

21:57.570 --> 21:59.250
Zhao will really marry someone else!

21:59.700 --> 22:00.570
And then?

22:00.570 --> 22:01.410
Then...

22:01.810 --> 22:03.530
Then Zhao'll spend her wedding night

22:03.530 --> 22:04.770
with that Zhou guy.

22:05.010 --> 22:06.090
Red veil lifted.

22:06.900 --> 22:08.050
Candles blown.

22:08.050 --> 22:09.330
You'll regret it soon enough.

22:13.750 --> 22:15.570
After word got out about
you going to the demon Sect,

22:16.250 --> 22:17.900
Mother's been urging me to check on you.

22:18.530 --> 22:20.420
I was worried
you'd be worn out from the trip,

22:20.420 --> 22:21.260
all alone.

22:21.660 --> 22:22.500
Now that I see you again,

22:22.900 --> 22:23.740
you really lost weight.

22:25.100 --> 22:26.570
On the eve of the Righteous-Demonic War,

22:27.090 --> 22:29.220
Lord Zhou actually married Miss Min.

22:29.770 --> 22:31.250
Even if your aunt was busy fighting evil

22:31.250 --> 22:32.330
and never married,

22:32.330 --> 22:33.980
he still jumped the gun, didn't he?

22:36.220 --> 22:37.180
Lately,

22:37.180 --> 22:38.980
I've been sorting through
my aunt's past.

22:38.980 --> 22:40.530
I wonder if your mother, Lady Min,

22:40.530 --> 22:42.180
was acquainted with my aunt.

22:42.180 --> 22:43.020
Whether they ever

22:43.730 --> 22:45.380
traveled somewhere together,

22:45.860 --> 22:47.180
or met anyone special?

22:51.010 --> 22:52.700
My mother has no time to go out.

22:53.940 --> 22:55.530
Father's focused on developing weapons

22:55.880 --> 22:57.140
and barely handles household affairs.

22:58.050 --> 22:59.250
We have grandmother,

22:59.770 --> 23:00.620
aunts,

23:00.620 --> 23:01.460
uncles,

23:01.620 --> 23:02.940
and uncles living under the same roof.

23:03.770 --> 23:05.140
Their daily needs,

23:05.140 --> 23:06.530
marriages, rituals

23:06.530 --> 23:08.180
are all managed by Mother alone.

23:08.180 --> 23:10.090
Whenever there are disputes
among the sisters-in-law,

23:10.090 --> 23:11.660
it is Mother who settles them.

23:11.660 --> 23:13.290
Social visits,

23:13.290 --> 23:14.660
shop inventories,

23:14.660 --> 23:15.770
accounting and petty affairs.

23:16.140 --> 23:17.490
Mother handles it all.

23:19.530 --> 23:20.730
Lady Min is truly capable.

23:21.290 --> 23:22.490
Mother always says

23:22.490 --> 23:23.940
Zhao is even more capable than she is.

23:24.380 --> 23:25.940
Once you marry into Peiqiong Manor,

23:26.320 --> 23:27.250
all this will be yours.

23:27.900 --> 23:28.860
From now on,

23:28.860 --> 23:31.010
you will be
the Manager of Peiqiong Manor.

23:33.120 --> 23:34.060
What's wrong with you?

23:35.380 --> 23:36.490
Your face looks a bit pale.

23:37.530 --> 23:38.370
Tired?

23:38.860 --> 23:40.010
A bit.

23:41.050 --> 23:42.730
Yuqi, this time you came here.

23:42.730 --> 23:43.660
Was it only to open a shop?

23:44.090 --> 23:45.330
I'm here to discuss

23:45.660 --> 23:46.530
our upcoming wedding

23:46.980 --> 23:48.620
with Lord Qi and the elders.

24:00.490 --> 24:01.330
Yuzhi,

24:03.520 --> 24:05.050
has Young Lord Zhou
been properly settled?

24:07.420 --> 24:08.570
Yuzhi, you're here for me?

24:10.700 --> 24:11.700
On this demon sect trip,

24:12.050 --> 24:13.250
as your senior brother,

24:13.530 --> 24:14.860
I failed to protect you.

24:16.900 --> 24:17.770
These handbooks

24:17.910 --> 24:19.940
are Jianghu tales and Six Sects' news
I gathered

24:19.940 --> 24:20.780
over the past half year.

24:20.980 --> 24:22.380
And many demon sect techniques.

24:23.490 --> 24:24.900
They might come in handy next time.

24:25.860 --> 24:26.810
Thank you, Yuzhi.

24:31.220 --> 24:32.490
You seems a bit down.

24:37.810 --> 24:39.220
I just realized

24:39.660 --> 24:40.940
that many things

24:41.820 --> 24:43.330
are hard
to align actions with beliefs.

24:44.220 --> 24:45.060
Zhao,

24:46.490 --> 24:47.500
is this marriage

24:48.660 --> 24:50.050
really what you want?

24:51.180 --> 24:52.380
The Qingque Sect breakthrough.

24:52.380 --> 24:53.620
The Bliss Palace battle.

24:53.620 --> 24:55.490
I knew then
you were an eagle, not a sparrow.

24:55.490 --> 24:56.900
You shouldn't be trapped
in a small space.

24:57.490 --> 24:58.620
If your heart already hesitates,

24:58.620 --> 25:00.290
why not find a better match?

25:00.810 --> 25:01.860
What about you, Yuzhi?

25:02.620 --> 25:03.770
Was your marriage what you wanted?

25:15.010 --> 25:16.380
It's all right, don't worry.

25:16.380 --> 25:18.010
Milady should be back soon.

25:18.010 --> 25:18.850
Xiaolan?

25:22.380 --> 25:23.700
Zhao, you're finally back.

25:26.220 --> 25:28.330
I made all these pastries myself.

25:28.980 --> 25:31.250
In a few days,
I'll return to the Siqi Sect.

25:31.700 --> 25:33.180
So I came to say goodbye.

25:33.570 --> 25:35.940
Thanks for taking care of me
at Qingque Sect.

25:36.140 --> 25:36.980
Xiaolan.

25:37.140 --> 25:38.290
Why are you leaving so soon?

25:38.990 --> 25:40.290
Is something wrong at the Siqi Sect?

25:47.250 --> 25:48.930
Nothing urgent, really.

25:49.660 --> 25:51.290
Father called me back

25:51.810 --> 25:53.000
to arrange a marriage.

25:53.380 --> 25:54.730
You're still so young.

25:55.330 --> 25:57.680
Why is your family rushing marriage?

25:57.900 --> 25:59.300
You may not know this, Zhao.

25:59.520 --> 26:00.900
My father's concubine is in charge.

26:01.330 --> 26:03.140
She sees me as an obstacle in her way.

26:03.140 --> 26:05.220
She's been urging Father
to marry me off early.

26:05.420 --> 26:06.950
But since Lord Yang is your Father,

26:07.420 --> 26:08.950
how can he treat you so unfairly?

26:09.290 --> 26:10.290
How is that biased?

26:11.490 --> 26:14.160
Father said he'd found me
a good husband's family.

26:14.620 --> 26:15.880
As long as I obey him,

26:16.220 --> 26:17.510
I'll live a worry-free life.

26:22.050 --> 26:23.900
But my mother lived like that.

26:24.570 --> 26:25.410
Followed every rule.

26:26.180 --> 26:27.290
Obeyed father before marriage,

26:27.290 --> 26:28.700
her husband after,

26:28.700 --> 26:29.570
living by his word.

26:29.570 --> 26:30.620
Remained faithful.

26:32.050 --> 26:33.570
Yet she compromised all her life

26:34.050 --> 26:34.940
and still met a bad end.

26:36.810 --> 26:38.380
I saw it with my own eyes.

26:38.940 --> 26:40.360
How can I believe

26:40.420 --> 26:42.540
that by following parents' will
and the matchmaker's words,

26:42.660 --> 26:44.010
I would find a perfect marriage?

26:44.660 --> 26:45.980
The world acts like

26:46.590 --> 26:48.450
marriage

26:48.720 --> 26:50.870
is the only important thing for women.

26:51.140 --> 26:52.350
Why can't women have

26:52.370 --> 26:53.870
their own dreams and aspirations?

26:54.570 --> 26:55.980
Ms. Cai made them come true.

26:55.980 --> 26:57.380
Then why, in this world,

26:57.380 --> 26:59.140
can't there be a second, a third,

26:59.140 --> 27:00.700
countless others like Ms. Cai?

27:04.220 --> 27:05.300
Aunt truly lived

27:05.770 --> 27:07.050
a life of justice.

27:09.700 --> 27:10.980
How will you handle it

27:11.550 --> 27:12.620
after returning to Siqi Sect?

27:15.130 --> 27:17.350
I'll try to negotiate with Father.

27:18.250 --> 27:19.860
After all, marriage is a serious matter.

27:19.860 --> 27:21.760
I need to follow my heart.

27:23.180 --> 27:24.020
Zhao,

27:24.380 --> 27:25.530
give your all in everything,

27:25.530 --> 27:26.570
and act from the heart.

27:28.900 --> 27:30.230
My Mother used to say

27:30.490 --> 27:31.920
the hardest thing is to choose.

27:32.350 --> 27:34.220
When faced with a tough decision,

27:34.420 --> 27:35.490
count to ten,

27:35.900 --> 27:37.010
calm down,

27:37.530 --> 27:39.380
and listen to your heart.

27:40.010 --> 27:41.140
Then you'll know what to do.

27:44.900 --> 27:45.770
Zhao.

27:45.770 --> 27:46.610
I'm leaving.

27:46.900 --> 27:47.770
Take care, Xiaolan.

28:19.290 --> 28:20.130
Zhao.

28:20.290 --> 28:21.130
Zhao.

28:22.530 --> 28:23.660
Why are you spacing out?

28:23.660 --> 28:24.860
Get up to collect gifts.

28:25.090 --> 28:25.930
What gifts?

28:38.490 --> 28:39.330
Min.

28:39.620 --> 28:40.530
Zhao.

28:42.050 --> 28:43.980
These were all sent by Yuqi?

28:43.980 --> 28:44.830
No.

28:44.840 --> 28:45.860
They were arranged by Aunt.

28:46.530 --> 28:47.380
After Yuqi left,

28:47.380 --> 28:49.570
Aunt spoke of Yuqi and Zhao's wedding.

28:50.490 --> 28:51.530
Aunt said

28:51.530 --> 28:52.940
you've always had a mind of your own,

28:53.490 --> 28:54.530
so you should check

28:54.530 --> 28:56.860
the betrothal gifts yourself.

28:57.250 --> 28:58.570
If anything's missing,

28:58.570 --> 28:59.980
we can make up for it in time.

28:59.980 --> 29:00.940
So

29:00.940 --> 29:02.330
she sent me to bring them.

29:02.770 --> 29:03.940
What a great husband's family.

29:04.330 --> 29:05.180
Zhao,

29:05.180 --> 29:06.290
you're so lucky.

29:09.010 --> 29:09.850
Min.

29:10.090 --> 29:11.090
Shouldn't my wedding

29:11.380 --> 29:13.330
wait until I finish my training?

29:13.860 --> 29:16.010
Why send the betrothal gifts so early?

29:17.140 --> 29:18.530
Aunt cares for you

29:19.180 --> 29:21.770
and hopes you'll marry soon.

29:25.050 --> 29:26.860
Marriage is a joyful thing.

29:26.860 --> 29:28.050
And my Mother said,

29:28.050 --> 29:29.140
when Zhao weds,

29:29.140 --> 29:31.220
the Qingque Sect must hold
a grand celebration.

29:31.420 --> 29:33.250
Come, let's see the gifts.

29:35.250 --> 29:36.490
This is the Mist Veil Canopy.

29:36.490 --> 29:38.090
Hang it in the room on hot days.

29:38.090 --> 29:39.530
The scent can keep mosquitoes away.

29:40.250 --> 29:42.010
Yuqi has one in his chamber.

29:44.290 --> 29:45.730
This is the Pine-Stone Inkstone.

29:45.730 --> 29:47.660
It's made from cliff iron pine.

29:47.660 --> 29:48.770
The ink smells fresh.

29:49.010 --> 29:50.770
Yuqi loves using it to copy scriptures.

29:51.010 --> 29:51.850
It calms the mind.

29:53.230 --> 29:54.330
This is the Fox Down Garment.

29:54.380 --> 29:56.050
It's made from
the softest down at a fox's neck.

29:56.420 --> 29:58.730
Yuqi wears it
next to his skin in winter.

30:01.290 --> 30:02.130
Wait.

30:02.570 --> 30:03.940
At first, I only thought

30:03.940 --> 30:06.250
Min was just closer to Mr. Mu.

30:06.660 --> 30:07.730
But now it seems

30:08.530 --> 30:09.770
your bond feels rather unusual.

30:11.050 --> 30:12.660
How's a girl supposed to know what her

30:12.660 --> 30:14.140
childhood friend wears underneath?

30:14.660 --> 30:16.490
I don't even know what Yuzhi wears.

30:16.770 --> 30:17.730
That kind of closeness.

30:17.730 --> 30:19.140
Quite out of the ordinary.

30:22.050 --> 30:22.900
Lingbo.

30:23.380 --> 30:25.380
I grew up alongside Yuqi.

30:25.770 --> 30:27.180
Naturally, I know what he likes.

30:28.290 --> 30:29.530
With what you just said,

30:29.810 --> 30:31.330
if someone with ill intent heard it,

30:31.800 --> 30:33.770
who knows
what misunderstandings will arise?

30:33.980 --> 30:36.010
You said it yourself.
How is it my fault?

30:36.770 --> 30:38.090
What's wrong with Peiqiong Manor,

30:38.420 --> 30:40.330
raising someone like you
who twists the truth?

30:40.620 --> 30:41.460
You...

30:41.700 --> 30:42.540
Lingbo.

30:42.770 --> 30:43.810
My bad for talking too much!

30:46.220 --> 30:47.570
Outdated goods.

30:59.180 --> 31:00.020
I'm so furious!

31:03.420 --> 31:04.380
I'm so furious!

31:04.380 --> 31:05.380
That Cai Zhao.

31:06.860 --> 31:07.700
I'm so mad.

31:10.660 --> 31:11.700
Already grown this much,

31:11.700 --> 31:13.940
yet still so reckless and rash.

31:13.940 --> 31:15.010
It's all because Cai Zhao.

31:15.570 --> 31:17.530
I tried to help her
deal with that Zhou clan's sister.

31:17.530 --> 31:18.370
But her?

31:18.660 --> 31:19.500
So ungrateful.

31:22.250 --> 31:23.180
Zhou clan's sister?

31:24.530 --> 31:26.010
Zhou Yuqi has a sister?

31:26.250 --> 31:27.490
It's that Min Xinrou.

31:28.140 --> 31:29.860
Cai Zhao really acts recklessly.

31:30.220 --> 31:31.770
With Min Xinrou around,

31:31.980 --> 31:33.140
she'll be in for trouble.

31:35.140 --> 31:35.980
Mother.

31:36.220 --> 31:38.490
I heard Min Xinrou's

31:38.490 --> 31:40.570
parents died young.
She was raised by the Zhou clan.

31:40.940 --> 31:42.700
And grew up with Zhou Yuqi.

31:43.180 --> 31:44.020
That makes sense.

31:44.490 --> 31:46.250
Their childhood bond

31:46.250 --> 31:47.620
is hard to interfere with by outsiders.

31:48.220 --> 31:50.220
No matter how glorious
Cai Zhao was before,

31:50.770 --> 31:52.050
after marrying into the Zhou clan,

31:52.650 --> 31:54.350
she'll be the mistress on the surface,

31:54.530 --> 31:55.660
but secretly,

31:55.660 --> 31:56.980
who knows what she'll be.

31:58.080 --> 31:59.380
I've told you countless times.

31:59.380 --> 32:00.570
You're a daughter of the Yin clan,

32:01.140 --> 32:03.290
the future Lady of Qingque Sect.

32:03.290 --> 32:06.010
Yet you spend your days
gossiping about others' private matters,

32:06.020 --> 32:07.180
spreading comments and rumors,

32:07.560 --> 32:08.980
aren't you afraid of losing your grace?

32:09.180 --> 32:10.060
Mother,

32:10.060 --> 32:11.180
why are you just like Father,

32:11.420 --> 32:12.940
always speaking up for Cai Zhao?

32:13.140 --> 32:14.220
It's because of you

32:14.420 --> 32:15.900
that she's so reckless.

32:20.300 --> 32:21.140
Mother,

32:21.340 --> 32:22.980
with Cai Zhao's fiery temper,

32:23.180 --> 32:24.380
once she marries into the Zhou clan,

32:24.860 --> 32:26.500
she'll turn the Zhou clan upside down.

32:29.180 --> 32:30.660
That's the least of it.

32:31.740 --> 32:33.700
Their marriage itself
might fall through.

32:34.340 --> 32:36.180
If their marriage really falls through,

32:36.580 --> 32:39.180
Milady's marriage with Mr. Song

32:39.530 --> 32:41.220
is bound to be affected.

32:41.660 --> 32:42.540
No way!

32:42.540 --> 32:43.700
What's yours is destined to be.

32:43.700 --> 32:45.140
No one can take it.

32:45.900 --> 32:47.380
But what's not

32:47.700 --> 32:49.260
can't be forced.

32:49.700 --> 32:50.540
Lingbo,

32:51.100 --> 32:52.580
do you insist on this?

33:01.020 --> 33:03.580
Madam has comforted Milady
several times.

33:04.220 --> 33:06.660
If she really can't let go of Mr. Song,

33:06.820 --> 33:07.660
why not

33:08.620 --> 33:09.980
help her again?

33:21.740 --> 33:22.580
Milady.

33:22.980 --> 33:24.860
These hairpins and rings.

33:24.860 --> 33:26.530
You rarely wear them when training.

33:26.790 --> 33:28.570
It's a waste to keep them locked up.

33:28.820 --> 33:31.060
Take whatever you like.

33:31.210 --> 33:33.080
Thank you, Milady!

33:33.820 --> 33:35.400
And these cloths, silk,

33:35.410 --> 33:36.810
books, and medicinal herbs.

33:36.820 --> 33:37.660
Where should I put them?

33:37.860 --> 33:38.700
Whatever.

33:38.940 --> 33:39.900
Up to you.

33:44.180 --> 33:45.020
Cai Zhao.

33:46.140 --> 33:47.900
What now, Lingbo?

33:48.220 --> 33:49.100
Want another fight?

33:49.660 --> 33:51.100
You still can't beat me.

33:52.780 --> 33:53.620
Alright.

33:54.620 --> 33:55.780
Everyone says you're clever.

33:55.880 --> 33:57.140
But to me, you seem truly foolish.

33:57.420 --> 33:58.940
Min Xinrou clearly...

33:58.940 --> 34:00.420
She likes Yuqi.

34:00.420 --> 34:01.300
You knew?

34:01.980 --> 34:03.220
I'm not blind.

34:03.220 --> 34:04.060
Then...

34:04.300 --> 34:05.380
You don't mind?

34:07.860 --> 34:09.740
You don't like Zhou Yuqi?

34:14.380 --> 34:15.220
Cai Zhao!

34:17.180 --> 34:18.020
Cai Zhao.

34:18.260 --> 34:19.620
I hate your

34:19.620 --> 34:20.940
detached attitude the most.

34:21.620 --> 34:23.500
Your fiancé has such a

34:23.500 --> 34:24.380
close female confidante.

34:24.660 --> 34:26.300
Don't tell me
you'd feel nothing in your heart.

34:27.380 --> 34:29.220
What if it were you, Lingbo?

34:29.620 --> 34:30.500
What would you do?

34:31.940 --> 34:32.980
Call off the engagement?

34:45.160 --> 34:55.820
=Generation to Generation=

35:14.580 --> 35:18.990
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

35:19.555 --> 35:24.170
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

35:24.510 --> 35:29.075
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

35:29.600 --> 35:33.900
♪Free to wander in the world♪

35:36.845 --> 35:41.545
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

35:42.070 --> 35:46.360
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

35:47.020 --> 35:51.050
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

35:51.365 --> 35:56.490
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

35:57.065 --> 36:01.875
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:02.090 --> 36:06.260
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

36:06.985 --> 36:10.920
♪I freely roam in the world♪

36:11.420 --> 36:16.695
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

36:39.425 --> 36:44.555
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:44.920 --> 36:49.290
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

36:49.555 --> 36:53.685
♪I freely roam in the world♪

36:53.870 --> 36:59.445
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
